          <li class="pull-right"><a href="https://github.com/google/guice">Google Guice</a></li>
  <p>Sisu is a set of <a href="https://github.com/google/guice" class="externalLink">Guice</a> modules that add classpath scanning, auto-binding, and dynamic wiring. Together these modules make up the Sisu container, but they can also be used individually.</p>
        &lt;artifactId&gt;guice&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  <p>Sisu looks for types annotated with <code>@Named</code>, binds them, and wires any missing dependencies.</p>
  // Standard JSR330 annotations
  import com.google.inject.Guice;
  import org.eclipse.sisu.space.SpaceModule;
  import org.eclipse.sisu.wire.WireModule;
  // Sisu will spot any @Named components
  @Named(&quot;One&quot;)
  @Named(&quot;Two&quot;)
  @Named(&quot;Three&quot;)
  @Named
    @Inject
      Guice.createInjector(
        new WireModule(                       // auto-wires unresolved dependencies
          new SpaceModule(                     // scans and binds @Named components
  <p>Sisu has a <a href="apidocs/org/eclipse/sisu/space/package-summary.html"><code>SpaceModule</code></a> for scanning and a <a href="apidocs/org/eclipse/sisu/wire/package-summary.html"><code>WireModule</code></a> that wires requests to its dynamic <a href="apidocs/org/eclipse/sisu/inject/package-summary.html"><code>BeanLocator</code></a>.</p>
[tool-exec] end id=call_T8513yTv1BoMFfUBIKu2GwNC|fc_00745f29079157b4016a3fd2c3e5408193a92495c921d15005 name=bash status=success
